WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.679 --> 00:00:15.235
Borovets like any other Bulgarien resort is famous because it is cheap , but cheap doesn't mean bad

00:00:15.471 --> 00:00:23.112
because here you can find many 5 stars hotels and the lift infrastructure is well developed.

00:00:31.658 --> 00:00:39.716
It is situated at just 75 km from Sofia , that means that you have to drive just one hour to get there.

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:51.200
Our first stop is near a very beautiful lake called Iskar.

00:01:29.013 --> 00:01:36.720
Samokov is the closest  city from Borovets at just 10 km so we stopped there to buy some stuff.

00:01:55.484 --> 00:02:01.683
Borovets known as Chamkoria until the middle of the 20th century was a haunting place for  the bulgarien kind ,

00:02:01.683 --> 00:02:13.588
now it is a popular Bulgarian mountain resort situated in Sofia Province, on the northern slopes of Rila, at an altitude of 1350 m.

00:02:40.911 --> 00:02:47.701
Accomodation  is great , almost all hotels are new with the  range between 3 and 5 stars.

00:03:09.785 --> 00:03:12.690
You can take one like this and get to the top.

00:03:34.938 --> 00:03:42.735
If you love mountain trips this is a very nice place for you ,I will choose the easy way , if you want you can choose the hard one.

00:03:51.111 --> 00:03:56.078
During the summer people come here for hiking , adventure , to hear the leaves ,

00:03:56.078 --> 00:04:06.275
to take some fresh air or just to make new friends , because ... here everything is full of life

00:05:24.796 --> 00:05:32.308
The lift infrastructure is new and very good , using the gondola u can get up to 2500 m altitude .

00:05:33.376 --> 00:05:43.198
The gondola lift has a capacity of 1200 persons per hour and  The journey takes around 20 minutes.

00:06:42.801 --> 00:06:50.763
60 km of marked pistes cover the generally north facing slopes up to an altitude of 2600 m,

00:06:29.028 --> 00:06:37.128
During the summer this is a very  quiet but during the winter it is very crowded 

00:06:51.208 --> 00:06:57.619
with many runs terminating near the village centre allowing skiers to ski almost to their hotel door.

00:06:58.342 --> 00:07:04.449
The longest run is a gentle 12 km return to the resort along the maintenance road.

00:07:11.013 --> 00:07:22.633
For night skiing there is a special lift pass that has to be bought separately at the kiosks on the pistes. It is valid from 5 pm till 10 pm.

